Package com.uk.tsl.rfid.asciiprotocol

Class DeviceProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.uk.tsl.rfid.asciiprotocol.DeviceProperties
  • public class DeviceProperties
extends java.lang.Object
    Devices can have command limits that are different than those supported by the ASCII Protocol e.g. Maximum Antenna power may vary between UHF reader devices This class provides access to these limits for the currently connected Device
